'''第21屆溫哥華影評人協會獎'''（The 21st Vancouver Film Critics Circle Awards）是[[溫哥華影評人協會|溫哥華影評人協會]]以茲獎勵[[2020年電影|2020年電影]]的獎項。國際電影類於2021年2月20日公布入圍名單<ref>{{cite news|url=https://vancouverfilmcritics.com/2021/02/20/mank-leads-the-vfcc-nominations-for-best-in-international-film/|title=MANK LEADS THE VFCC NOMINATIONS FOR BEST IN INTERNATIONAL FILM|publisher=[[溫哥華影評人協會|溫哥華影評人協會]]|author=Jorge Ignacio Castillo|date=2021-02-20|accessdate=2021-02-23|archive-date=2021-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223110901/https://vancouverfilmcritics.com/2021/02/20/mank-leads-the-vfcc-nominations-for-best-in-international-film/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2月22日宣布得獎者<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/chloe-zhaos-nomadland-named-best-feature-by-vancouver-film-critics-circle|title=Chloe Zhao's 'Nomadland' Named Best Feature by Vancouver Film Critics Circle|publisher=[[荷里活報道|好萊塢報導]]|author=Etan Vlessing|date=2021-02-22|accessdate=2021-02-23|archive-date=2021-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210222150040/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/chloe-zhaos-nomadland-named-best-feature-by-vancouver-film-critics-circle|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://vancouverfilmcritics.com/2021/03/12/vancouver-film-critics-circle-name-nomadland-best-international-feature/|title=VANCOUVER FILM CRITICS CIRCLE NAME NOMADLAND BEST INTERNATIONAL FEATURE|publisher=溫哥華影評人協會|author=Jorge Ignacio Castillo|date=2021-03-12|accessdate=2021-03-21|archive-date=2021-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420051431/https://vancouverfilmcritics.com/2021/03/12/vancouver-film-critics-circle-name-nomadland-best-international-feature/}}</ref>。加拿大電影類於2月3日宣布入圍名單<ref>{{cite news|url=https://vancouverfilmcritics.com/2021/02/03/possessor-and-chained-dominate-the-vfcc-nominations-for-best-in-canadian-film/|title=POSSESSOR AND CHAINED DOMINATE THE VFCC NOMINATIONS FOR BEST IN CANADIAN FILM|publisher=溫哥華影評人協會|author=Jorge Ignacio Castillo|date=2021-02-03|accessdate=2021-03-21|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421012224/https://vancouverfilmcritics.com/2021/02/03/possessor-and-chained-dominate-the-vfcc-nominations-for-best-in-canadian-film/}}</ref>，3月8日公布得獎者<ref>{{cite news|url=https://vancouverfilmcritics.com/2021/03/12/vancouver-film-critics-circle-name-violation-best-canadian-feature/|title=VANCOUVER FILM CRITICS CIRCLE NAME VIOLATION BEST CANADIAN FEATURE|publisher=溫哥華影評人協會|author=Jorge Ignacio Castillo|date=2021-03-12|accessdate=2021-03-21|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421140543/https://vancouverfilmcritics.com/2021/03/12/vancouver-film-critics-circle-name-violation-best-canadian-feature/}}</ref>。

